{"id":29123,"date":"2019-05-10T22:33:42","date_gmt":"2019-05-10T18:33:42","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=29123"},"modified":"2024-01-08T10:46:36","modified_gmt":"2024-01-08T06:46:36","slug":"taqwa-sum-of-all-good","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/10\/taqwa-sum-of-all-good\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Taqwa: Be mindful of Allah as it is sum of all good"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: A man came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, instruct me.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>You must fear Allah, for it is the sum of all good. You must wage jihad in the way of Allah, for it is the monasticism of the Muslims. You must remember Allah and recite His Book, for it will be your light upon the earth and your mention in the heavens. You must hold your tongue unless it is good, for by it you will defeat Satan<\/strong>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: al-Mu&#8217;jam al-S\u0323aghi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 949<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih li ghayrihi<\/em><\/strong> (authentic due to external evidence) according to Al-Albani<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064e \u0631\u064e\u062c\u064f\u0644\u064c \u0625\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0622\u0644\u0650\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u064